  "text": "Following the identification, in 1995 and 1996, of the first three LQTS genes associated with the most frequently encountered LQTS variants called respectively LQT1, LQT2, and LQT3, there has been a flourishing of identifications of genes proven or just thought to be associated with LQTS [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] . This includes the genes for LQT4 through LQT10 (Table 1) .",
